<p>The Adult Cystic Fibrosis (CF) Unit is part of <a href="">King&#8217;s Adult CF Service</a> and provides specialist inpatient care. It&#8217;s on Lonsdale Ward and has nine single rooms with bathroom facilities as well as a treatment room for patients having annual reviews or day care.</p>
